                <Label TextColor="Wheat" BackgroundColor="BlueViolet" FontSize="Title">net-stop</Label>
                <Label>net-stop creates a queue in wich incoming packets to the traget with the spoofer are held and dropped so the target never gets a response.</Label>
                <Label TextColor="Wheat" BackgroundColor="BlueViolet" FontSize="Title">dns-spoof</Label>
